{"text": " Welcome to the three-minute guided meditation training by all here. We will now begin five rounds consisting of three minutes each with one minute pause in between. We shall begin the first round in ten seconds. Round one. Visualize the cosmic sky. Look at the night sky. See the stars, look at the darkness. See the cosmic sky. Allow the stars to move closer to you and look at the dark space between the stars. Look at the darkness. Allow the stars to shift away as you move towards darkness. Look at the stars, look at the darkness. See the dark space. Look at the darkness, approach your face. Look at the dark space. And round one.", "segments": [{"id": 0, "seek": 0, "start": 3.4, "end": 12.42, "text": " Welcome to the three-minute guided meditation training by all here.", "tokens": [50364, 4027, 281, 264, 1045, 12, 18256, 19663, 12537, 3097, 538, 439, 510, 13, 50984], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.5552269991706399, "compression_ratio": 0.9852941176470589, "no_speech_prob": 0.02909237891435623, "words": [{"word": " Welcome", "start": 3.4, "end": 4.8, "probability": 0.7407909035682678}, {"word": " to", "start": 4.8, "end": 5.68, "probability": 0.9503063559532166}, {"word": " the", "start": 5.68, "end": 5.82, "probability": 0.9422826170921326}, {"word": " three", "start": 5.82, "end": 6.14, "probability": 0.47241315245628357}, {"word": "-minute", "start": 6.14, "end": 6.44, "probability": 0.7987883687019348}, {"word": " guided", "start": 6.44, "end": 8.16, "probability": 0.9675061106681824}, {"word": " meditation", "start": 8.16, "end": 9.0, "probability": 0.9282737970352173}, {"word": " training", "start": 9.0, "end": 9.86, "probability": 0.9894132018089294}, {"word": " by", "start": 9.86, "end": 11.08, "probability": 0.6181202530860901}, {"word": " all", "start": 11.08, "end": 11.42, "probability": 0.9032564163208008}, {"word": " here.", "start": 11.42, "end": 12.42, "probability": 0.984860360622406}]}, {"id": 1, "seek": 1242, "start": 20.84, "end": 